# Policies Created

## 1. TestBucketAccess

This custom policy was created to allow bucket access for selected IAM users.

Permissions included:

* s3:GetObject
* s3:ListBucket
* s3:PutObject

This policy was attached to:

* Alpha
* s3-user

---

## 2. DenyTestBucketAccess

This policy was created to restrict bucket access for unauthorized users.

Explicit Deny permissions were applied for:

* billing-user
* developer-user
* admin-user

The policy restricted:

* Bucket access
* Object access
* Bucket listing

